<a href="/eq/board?board.id=Crier">The Town Crier (Announcements)</a> - <a href="/eq/board/message?board.id=Crier&message.id=119">Your Halfling E3 Report 5/18/2005</a><p>


		<table cellpadding=4 cellspacing=0 border=1 width="100%">
			<tr>
				<td>&nbsp;</td><td>Your Halfling E3 Report 5/18/2005</td></tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="msg_user_cell" width="200" valign=top>
				
					<img src='/i/rank_icons/moderator.gif' border=0 alt=''> <span style='color:#FF0000;font-weight:bold; '>Ashlanne</span>
