<P><IMG src="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/images/forum_images/e3/Booth_babe_PSP.jpg"></P>
<P>Larger Versions of this poster could be found in several places at the show...&nbsp; Wonder if I could get one for the office I share with Ky <img src='/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-wink.gif' width=16 height=16 border=0></P>
